REG_{T}=\sum_{t=1}^{T}\mu(\xb_{t,*}^{\top}\theta_{*})-\sum_{t=1}^{T}\mu(X_{t}^{\top}\theta_{*}).
\]

\end_inset

where 
\begin_inset Formula $\xb_{t,*}=\arg\min_{\xb\in\Xcal_{t}}\mu(\xb^{\top}\theta_{*})$
\end_inset

 is the optimal action.
 Besides,
 we have the following standard boundedness assumptions used in the GLB literature
